narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: IF YOU'RE INTERESTED IN PUERTO RICO, LATIN AMERICA OR THE CARIBBEAN: YES. DEFINITELY.
If interested in the literature of Puerto Rico, take it. If interested in literary colonial responses to imperialism, take it.
